            "description": "The freelancer was unable to complete the project assigned and left us hanging for more than necessary. Offered an alternative solution, the freelancer gave us an esteem of the time it would have taken to complete the project that was out of our tolerance. Still, we may want to give them a second chance if we happen to have a task which we believe to be within their reach.\r\nI put 2 stars in communication not for the quality of it, but because they did not tell us they were unable to complete the task until it was too late.\n\n[11 November, 2021] They told us the app would have been completed by January(in September), but after a long time in which communication has been slow we reached November and they said they were not able to build on NextCloud.\nI've asked them about an esteem if a different approach was taken. They esteemed it to be ready by end of March. Which was deemed unacceptable. \nWe will complete the project on our own. \nWe may decide to give them a second chance if we happen to have a project within their reach.",
