            "role": "freelancer",
            "status": "active",
            "time_submitted": 1553970822,
            "description": "What a waste of time and money.\n\nIve written in angularJS for years but wanted to use angular9 which is very different and the CLI proved too much for me to wrap my head around.\n\nTo start, all I wanted them to do was make my html/css UI work using angular9 MVC so i could show a prototype to a client.\n\nOf course as soon as they were awarded the project, communication dropped off. when asking questions about their broken code i was told \"we cant explain to you, either give us a task or we need to give attention to other projects\". But once given tasks, I would have to spend hours explaining things to them and then have to pay for them to redo work theyd done wrong, only to find that id paid for it to be done wrong again!\n\nI asked for MY CODE to be built into an MVC and despite multiple times telling them NOT to use bootstrap they ignored me and argued that it \"allows reliable and consistent component creation\" so they screwed up my entire UI in an unsuccessful attempt to turn it into a modified bootstrap layout. which I EXPLICITLY TOLD THEM NOT TO DO.\n\nThen they would blame me when their code didn't work claiming I installed libraries or npms that I hadn't, and when id tell them to just make it work as promised, I'd get billed for more time, for code that STILL DIDN'T WORK.\n\nAfter wasting 3 weeks and $250, I told them to stop working and cancelled the project.\n\nI've since written this in Angular 1.7.8 and 2 hours of coding was all it took. I wish id never have used this team.",
