            "description": "Narola Infotech does a wonderful job on there work and have worked with me day and night to understand my project, my business and how the project will impact my business. I would recommend them to anyone for web development work. The web developer that worked on my project provided me with good work and a secure web platform to access my app, which was built with a robust backend. My only complaints are that I had to request some work repeatedly during the process, there was not always good understanding when there was a developer scheduled for my web platform and when there was not, daily update frequency and reliability declined. Lastly, my deadlines did not seem to be taken seriously and there were multiple points where the project manager, Prerna, said that a feature or assignment or estimate for how long something would take were supposed to be delivered to me but I would not receive them and when I followed up about them, there was stalling and some mails seemed to have been lost in her inbox. This was frustrating but it did not overshadow their wonderful work on this project. The reason this persisted as my fault, as I did not provide them weekly feedback through Freelancer. Overall, working with Narola is a wonderful experience and very professional. I am sure if I had provided weekly feedback, these problems I had would not have repeated themselves and would be unlikely to happen. I can tell you now that I will indeed work with them again.",
