            "description": "Very good company and they work as a nice professional team.\n\n[12 March, 2017] Did fairly well though I feel that the quality can be improved. To be fair it is quite a complex project and I am sure the developer is doing the absolute best but I am sure there is always room for improvement. I am aware that i am not asking for the everyday joe website though thats why I like to keep pushing to the absolute best possible!\n\n[15 March, 2017] I choose to stay with this freelancer as they delivered good what I asked for a booking system. However now things are getting complex with JS, one page, database requests and AJAX. The developer is trying his best to keep up with my requirements however I feel that things can be improved. Other than that I am satisfied as this is a solid company that works in unison and if also one dev gets sick a replacement is found. I think is good value for money.\n\n[29 March, 2017] On time and getting better and better. They had a really tough project to complete and together with my help we tried for the best.",
