            "role": "freelancer",
            "status": "active",
            "time_submitted": 1490204035,
            "description": "winmaclin (Narola Tech) is very capable of dealing with most average websites. Our site has 34 plugins, including social logins, a social network (Buddypress), Events Management, advanced group functionality (group hierarchies), and heavy modification to out-of-the-box user capabilities. While Narola was able to handle the projects we assigned, they were not all completed smoothly. On several occasions, their solutions ended up breaking other parts of our site, and required additional time to correct their original solutions. More involved QA testing would probably have caught these issues. Having said that, it's important to note that Narola is inexpensive for the quality of work received. If your site is simple to moderately complex, they are a good value for your money.",
