            "description": "I would have no reservations recommending winmaclin to anyone who requires their services designing a website. \r\n\r\nHaving previously had a very bad job done for me from another freelancer on another platform, It was very important for me that the freelancer working on my project would communicate well with me regarding my project outcomes and I got exactly that. On many occasions we had extended periods of communication to make sure that design issues and functionality. In addition, I found it very helpful also that the I could consult the freelancer for alternate ideas/implementation that would eventually give the same result if my initial design idea wasn't sufficient. \r\n\r\nI'm quite confident that they will be able to deliver to the same level of professionalism and quality for other people. And I will be willing to engage their services again.\n\n[17 November, 2016] I'm glad that I got Winmaclin to work on my project. it took longer than I expected due to certain unforeseen difficulties. But in all, I am very grateful for the effort in matters of work quality and also communication. I'll definitely recommend their service.\n\n[04 January, 2017] Whatever the goal of my project,communication is very important. With Winmaclin, I can say confidently that they have exceeded my expectation in terms of communication.  And beyond that, the delivery was excellent. I'll definitely hire them again",
